creator: SpotMe
descriptionHtml:
The SpotMe Hybrid engagement app turns lectures and content into conversations, conversations into connections and connections into collaborations, across teams, groups, and continents.

From in-person to virtual meetings or a hybrid of both, SpotMe delivers the same seamless and tailored experience to your users.

Streaming, Video breakout sessions, message, video chat,, exchange digital business cards, schedule meetings, complete surveys, create personal agendas, participate in live Q&A and polling sessions, study virtual libraries and meeting information, review case studies, browse speaker and attendee profiles, follow presentations, take notes, save items for after your event, and much more.

The SpotMe event app is suitable for meetings of all sizes, from large medical congresses to focused business leadership forums. Professionals from leading companies rely on SpotMe to drive ideation, gather audience response, encourage networking, team building, strategy rollouts, and education at their high-stakes events.

NOTE - You must be a registered participant with a valid email address or alternative to use this app.
descriptionShort: One app for all your events.
